# Runtime deploy state — rewritten by deploy.sh on every blue/green flip,
# so keeping it tracked makes every host-side `git pull` abort with a dirty
# working tree. The bootstrap path in deploy.sh writes the initial value
# (`reverse_proxy app-blue:8000`) when the file is absent; the
# upstream.conf.example next to it is the human-readable reference shape.
deploy/upstream.conf
